    {
      "id": "bdac8a8d-e234-46db-be2f-60d74dc64ced",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Effectuer la division suivant les puissances croissantes {\\`a} un ordre\n    queclonque de $1-X^2$ par $1 - 2X\\cos\\theta + X^2$.",
        "html": "<p>Effectuer la division suivant les puissances croissantes <span>à</span> un ordre queclonque de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1-X^2\\)</span> par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 - 2X\\cos\\theta + X^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "77fbbd2d-f56a-4365-b1a4-f82c99358ee3",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$1-X^2 = (1-2X\\cos\\theta+X^2)(1 + 2X\\cos\\theta + \\dots + 2X^n\\cos n\\theta)\n                    + 2X^{n+1}\\cos(n+1)\\theta - 2X^{n+2}\\cos n\\theta$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(1-X^2 = (1-2X\\cos\\theta+X^2)(1 + 2X\\cos\\theta + \\dots + 2X^n\\cos n\\theta)\n                    + 2X^{n+1}\\cos(n+1)\\theta - 2X^{n+2}\\cos n\\theta\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3788f254-e96a-48c5-86f7-b015a481dfcb",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire la valeur de $1 + 2\\sum_{k=1}^n \\cos k\\theta$,\n    ($\\theta \\not\\equiv 0 (\\mathrm{mod}\\,{2\\pi})$).",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire la valeur de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 + 2\\sum_{k=1}^n \\cos k\\theta\\)</span>, (<span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\theta \\not\\equiv 0 (\\mathrm{mod}\\,{2\\pi})\\)</span>).</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "832f747f-2c06-4a1a-881f-183e91f17fbf",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$=\\frac{\\cos n\\theta - \\cos(n+1)\\theta}{1-\\cos\\theta}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(=\\frac{\\cos n\\theta - \\cos(n+1)\\theta}{1-\\cos\\theta}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
